</header>

<!-- ABOUT CONTENT -->
<main class="container my-5">

    <!-- Project Overview -->
    <div class="card card-custom p-4 mb-4">
        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Project Overview</h4>
        <p>
            This project is a front-end web application developed to assist students in
            exploring potential career paths and evaluating their skill readiness based
            on personal interests, strengths, and self-identified skills.
        </p>

        <p>
            The system processes user input using JavaScript logic and provides structured
            career recommendations and readiness feedback without relying on backend
            processing or databases.
        </p>

    </div>

    <!-- Project Objectives -->
    <div class="card card-custom p-4 mb-4">
        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Project Objectives</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>To assist students in exploring suitable career paths</li>
            <li>To assess skill readiness through structured self-evaluation</li>
            <li>To apply usability and interface design principles</li>
            <li>To present career-related information clearly and accessibly</li>
        </ul>

    </div>

    <!-- Learning Outcomes -->
    <div class="card card-custom p-4 mb-4">
        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Learning Outcomes</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>Develop an interactive front-end application</li>
            <li>Apply Shneiderman’s 8 Golden Rules in interface design</li>
            <li>Use JavaScript to process user input and logic</li>
            <li>Present information clearly and accessibly</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Technologies Used -->
    <div class="card card-custom p-4 mb-4">
        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Technologies Used</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>HTML5 – Structure of the web pages</li>
            <li>CSS3 – Styling, layout, and responsiveness</li>
            <li>JavaScript – User interaction and logic processing</li>
            <li>Bootstrap 5 – Responsive layout and UI components</li>
        </ul>

    </div>

    <!-- Design Justification -->
    <div class="card card-custom p-4 mb-4">
        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Design Justification</h4>
        <p>
            The portal interface follows Shneiderman’s 8 Golden Rules by maintaining
            consistency in layout, providing clear feedback through interactive
            elements, supporting user control, and ensuring a clean, readable design.
        </p>
        <p>
            Responsive layouts and accessible colour themes enhance usability across
            devices and screen sizes.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Group Members -->
    <div class="card card-custom p-4">
